\c 120
\s Munyengetero womunhu ari pakutambudzika
\d Rwiyo rworwendo.
\p
\v 1 Pakutambudzika kwangu ndakadana kuna Jehovha, iye akandipindura.
\v 2 Rwirai mweya wangu, Jehovha, pamiromo inoreva nhema, naparurimi runonyengedzera.
\v 3 Iwe uchapiweiko, chinyi chichawedzerwa kwauri, iwe rurimi runonyengedzera?
\v 4 Miseve inopinza yeanesimba, namazimbe anopfuta omurara.
\p
\v 5 Ndine ropa rakaipa zvandiri mutorwa paMesheki, zvandigere pamatende eKedhari!
\v 6 Mweya wangu wakagara nguva refu neanovenga rugare.
\v 7 Ini ndinoda rugare; asi kana ndichitaura, ivo vanotsvaka kurwa.
